Alembic migration environment (single-database configuration).

The database URL is supplied dynamically by env.py from the application's
Settings (app.core.config), not from alembic.ini.

Common commands (run from the backend/ directory with the venv active):

    # Autogenerate a new migration after changing the ORM models:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe the change"

    # Apply all pending migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

    # Revert the most recent migration:
    alembic downgrade -1
